            . I am a pawnbroker, and live in Bishopsgate-street. On the 23d of May the prisoner pledged a table-spoon with me for eight shillings. I believe him to be the man. He has had his head shaved since, which alters his appearance.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180617-8-person111">
                  JAMES 
                  FOREST
