                  </persName>
            . I lived at the Cock and Magpie, in Drury-lane, the prisoner was in the habit of coming there; he came and asked me to pledge a shawl, which I did, in Drury-lane, and he gave me the duplicate of the two spoons.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180617-8-person112">
